description.text:
(Translated from Chinese by AI)
1. Fixed the issue where Neoforge 26.1+ could not be parsed;  
2. Corrected some text errors;  
3. Fixed the issue where the missing old stb API caused certain mods (JourneyMap/Meteor Client) to malfunction;  
4. Removed the log copying feature;  
5. Fixed a crash issue that could occur when displaying logs;  
6. Fixed the issue where the GUI inside Axiom could not be clicked;  
7. Removed the portable/global account switching button.
